text: Desmiphoropsis variegata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Audinet-Serville in 1835. It is known from Argentina and Brazil.BioLib.cz - Desmiphoropsis variegata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1835
